summary: Inktober is about experimenting, so here's an experiment with colour and probably only the second time i have drawn a super...

Inktober is about experimenting, so here’s an experiment with colour and probably only the second time i have drawn a super hero.

Coloured pencils, promarker, pen, ink and white out pen + screentone for her suit.
